key goals of the game include:
	it should be hard to conquer the world
	it is easier to defend than to attack
	it takes a long time to make all regions produce a lot of income and powerful units
	it's expensive to have huge armies
	it's reasonable to develop some regions and not develop others

future goals:
	war should not be the only aspect of the gameplay; diplomacy, economy, trade, etc. should also play a part

