battering ram - makes assault conceivable; useful because it can hardly be destroyed by shooters
balista - makes troops inside garrison vulnerable (which often means they have to attack)
ditch - slows down movement
moat - makes battering ram mostly useless
	TODO how to enter the garrison after the wall is destroyed? siege tower?

shooters should be weaker against better garrison

